<item>
            <title>[LOG4J2-81] PatternLayout appender not respecting format modifiers</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-81</link>
                <project id="12310790" key="LOG4J2">Log4j 2</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Example pattern:&lt;br/&gt;
[%d&lt;/p&gt;
{yyyyMMdd HH:mm:ss,SSS}
&lt;p&gt;] %-5p [%-25.25c&lt;/p&gt;
{1}:%-4L] - %m%n&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
Text output is:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;20120907 14:18:36,875&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; INFO [XXXXXX...&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;20120907 14:18:36,875&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; INFO [XXXXXX...&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;20120907 14:18:36,965&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; ERROR [XXXXX...&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
NOTE that &quot;INFO&quot; and &quot;ERROR&quot; are not left justified for 5 spaces (%-5p)&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
The logger name ([%-25.25c{1}
&lt;p&gt;) is not left justified or padded when there are less then 25 characters&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The line number is not left justified or padded either (%-4L)&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;not applicable&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
